description:
He leadeth me "Karaoke /Instrumental" (Low Key). He hath anoint me to sing unto the Lord, with thanksgiving. I will always remember all the good times I've had with Him- singing karaoke! This gospel karaoke is perfect for any personal or small group gathering. Let Him take you where you want to go- in His perfect timing.

First Line: He leadeth me: O blessed thought!
Title: He Leadeth Me
Author: J. H. Gilmore (1862)
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters' karaoke youtube
